      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The logs strongly suggest that the 500 errors are caused by your application timing out while trying to communicate with the `payment-gateway-auth` service. Since this happens during peak traffic, the downstream service is likely becoming overloaded and unable to respond to requests within your configured 10-second timeout limit. You should investigate the resource utilization and latency of the `payment-gateway-auth` service first. To mitigate this immediately, consider increasing the client-side timeout temporarily or implementing a circuit breaker pattern.",
